\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca123dd7b68be70dad1304606dc53f1d719b7d03","tid":1738914,"uid":334806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T11:52:15.000Z","msg":"民主黨前立法會議員傍晚時分在天后港鐵站附近遇襲，他已被送律頓治醫院。何俊仁接受《蘋果》訪問時稱，他傍晚坐港鐵回家，離開天后站時已有市民提醒他，站外有數名黑衣人，他當時不以為意，詎料黑衣人跟隨他，行到附近橫街即在身後向他襲擊，他的頭及背部被人打傷，黑衣人見得手後即逃走，何俊仁事後往律敦治醫院求醫。"},{"pid":"988cae61d03621fd48f799f53a7477ec8063d9c1","tid":1738914,"uid":34863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T12:26:38.000Z","msg":"有暗影。。。"},{"pid":"7c60919d840979339211fd7258a31765f8f2bfbc","tid":1738914,"uid":21028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T12:27:14.000Z","msg":"佢又被人打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cdd639ea04e9f1b6dea8e05fc9bb118574351af","tid":1738914,"uid":335335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T12:32:13.000Z","msg":"AV<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}